entry.value: Input table (may contain also columns not to be normalized)

Data normalization metanode using nonlinear normalization techniques.%%00010%%00010Currently implements quantile, vsn and loess (with 3 different methods) techniques. Consult e.g. limma R package for details on each normalization technique.%%00010%%00010You can select what columns should be processed by the metanode, no need to preselect them before the node.%%00010%%00010The node returns only selected columns after applied normalization with the same table header.%%00010%%00010=================%%00010%%00010Used programs and tools and their respective licenses at the time of the metanode creation.
